# ============================================================
# CastON — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values.
# ============================================================

# Supabase (optional)
# Required for: remote regulations update checks (app works fully without this)
# Not required for: weather, solunar, FMZ detection, regulations (bundled), species info
#
# Setup: create a free project at https://supabase.com
#   1. Create a public Storage bucket named "data"
#   2. Upload public/data/regulations-2025.json as "regulations.json" to that bucket
#   3. Copy your Project URL and anon key from Settings → API
#
# Get these from: https://supabase.com/dashboard/project/_/settings/api
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here

# ============================================================
# No other env vars are required.
# Weather data: Open-Meteo (free, no API key)
# Water temp: ECCC Hydrometric API (free, proxied via /api/watertemp)
# Moon/solunar: SunCalc (client-side, no API key)
# Geocoding: OpenStreetMap Nominatim (free, no API key)
# ============================================================
